OL,3,CIn full: Andy Burnham's first speech
OL,4,Cas prime minister
OL,6,FWatch Andy Burnham's speech in full
OL,8,FAndy Burnham delivered his first
OL,9,Fspeech as prime minister outside
OL,10,FDowning Street on Monday.
OL,12,FAfter being appointed by King Charles
OL,13,Fat Buckingham Palace, he headed to
OL,14,FNumber 10, where he was met with
OL,15,Fcheers and applause.
OL,17,FRead his full speech here:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784569707
OL,3,CIn full: Andy Burnham's first speech
OL,4,Cas prime minister
OL,6,F"I have just come from Buckingham
OL,7,FPalace, where I have accepted His
OL,8,FMajesty the King's invitation to form
OL,9,Fa Government.
OL,11,F"In doing so, I am acutely conscious
OL,12,Fthat I am the sixth person in the last
OL,13,F10 years to walk up this street, the
OL,14,Fseventh prime minister since 2016,
OL,15,Fmaking this a moment for reflection
OL,16,Fand new resolution.
OL,18,F"It requires my generation of
OL,19,Fpoliticians to raise our game and rise
OL,20,Fto the new challenge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784569707
OL,3,CIn full: Andy Burnham's first speech
OL,4,Cas prime minister
OL,6,F"Britain needs to show the world that
OL,7,Fwe can regain our stability once
OL,8,Fagain, and that is our challenge ` to
OL,9,Fmake politics work, to make it work
OL,10,Fbetter.
OL,12,F"I know people at home are fed up with
OL,13,Fpolitics. I hear you and I want to be
OL,14,Fhonest with you ` we have not been
OL,15,Fgood enough, and we need to be better.
OL,16,FWe will be. We will make this moment a
OL,17,Fcircuit breaker for Britain, bringing
OL,18,Fforward the biggest changes in the
OL,19,Flast 40 years ` a new political model
OL,20,Fand a new economic model.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784569707
OL,3,CIn full: Andy Burnham's first speech
OL,4,Cas prime minister
OL,6,F"In the 1980s, Britain took some wrong
OL,7,Fturns. Political power was
OL,8,Fcentralised, economic power
OL,9,Fprivatised, large parts of the country
OL,10,Fdeindustrialised, and they still
OL,11,Fhaven't recovered.
OL,13,F"Many feel as though they're still in
OL,14,Fdecline and they don't have the
OL,15,Fability to turn things around. And
OL,16,Fthat's why we will change politics to
OL,17,Fmake it more collaborative, more about
OL,18,Fproblem solving than point scoring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784569707
OL,3,CIn full: Andy Burnham's first speech
OL,4,Cas prime minister
OL,6,F"And we will take power out of here,
OL,7,Fand carry it into every postcode in
OL,8,Fthe land, so that they can do more,
OL,9,Fand in doing more, build a new
OL,10,Feconomy, where we put life's
OL,11,Fessentials back under stronger public
OL,12,Fcontrol to make them affordable to you
OL,13,Fagain, reindustrialising Britain using
OL,14,Fpublic procurement to back British
OL,15,Findustry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784569707
OL,3,CIn full: Andy Burnham's first speech
OL,4,Cas prime minister
OL,6,F"Later this year, I will bring forward
OL,7,Fa new plan for Britain, a 10-year
OL,8,Fplan, laying out a path from where we
OL,9,Fare now to where I believe we all want
OL,10,FBritain to be, wherever we're coming
OL,11,Ffrom, whatever party we support.
OL,13,F"But I can do something to give people
OL,14,Fsome breathing space now, some help
OL,15,Fwith the cost of living, and I will
OL,16,Fset out some of those measures
OL,17,Fstarting tomorrow, including how we
OL,18,Fpay for them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784569707
OL,3,CIn full: Andy Burnham's first speech
OL,4,Cas prime minister
OL,6,F"We will help more young people into
OL,7,Fwork by changing the education system
OL,8,Fand giving them more support, more
OL,9,Fmental health support, and we will
OL,10,Fbuild more council homes.
OL,12,F"That is the fair and sustainable way
OL,13,Fto bring the welfare bill down, to
OL,14,Fmeet our fiscal rules, and to honour
OL,15,Four commitments on defence to our
OL,16,Finternational partners.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784569707
OL,3,CIn full: Andy Burnham's first speech
OL,4,Cas prime minister
OL,6,F"We will help people to live well,
OL,7,Fbuilding a more preventative state,
OL,8,Finvesting in people's success rather
OL,9,Fthan paying for failure, and that work
OL,10,Fstarts now.
OL,12,F"I will soon go through that door
OL,13,Fbehind me and issue my first
OL,14,Finstruction to end rough sleeping in
OL,15,Four country.
OL,17,F"It's about putting the right values
OL,18,Fand the right standards at the heart
OL,19,Fof government. I will put the care of
OL,20,Fpeople at the heart of everything I do.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784569707
OL,3,CIn full: Andy Burnham's first speech
OL,4,Cas prime minister
OL,6,F"I will give this my all, and I ask
OL,7,Fyou all to pull with me. Let's build a
OL,8,Fnew national sense of unity, of common
OL,9,Fpurpose, and positivity.
OL,11,F"Let us make this the moment when
OL,12,FBritain starts to believe again, the
OL,13,Fmoment we bring back hope.
OL,15,F"Thank you very much, everybody."
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
